        <description><![CDATA[<b>Yunaska (363)</b><br/>2022 — Aleutian Islands<br/><b>5 passes</b><br/><br/><b>Pass 1</b> (Jul 10): FMC error - don't use this pass; ~10 animals jumped off rock and ~30 disturbed on rookery beach<br/><b>Pass 2</b> (Jul 10): Haulout beach; surveyed at 1000' to prevent disturbance<br/><b>Pass 3</b> (Jul 10): Rookery beach; surveyed 1000'<br/><b>Pass 4</b> (Jul 10): Right of Pass 3; surveyed at 1000'<br/><b>Pass 5</b> (Jul 10)]]></description>
